
You should install the various dashboard files from this directory in an appropriate
location in your grafana installation after all of the components have been plumbed in.

You will need a running prometheus and grafana instance and to invoke your za application with an appropriate CIDR list with metrics enabled.

E.g.:

  ZA_PROMETHEUS_CIDR="0.0.0.0/0" ZA_PROMETHEUS=9091 za script_name

  # script_name:eg/web for example
  # ZA_PROMETHEUS enables the exporter and sets the port number to serve the exports from, i.e. 0.0.0.0:9091 in the example above.
  # you should also provide a more restrictive CIDR for your prometheus server if possible.



